{"tid":1831444,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢肺炎病例增至217宗　廣東省有14宗","createTime":"2020-01-20T11:44:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T11:54:16.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"68cba3aecfe05eaee424dd379afd1c608bddcba0","tid":1831444,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T11:44:04.000Z","msg":"內地新型肺炎病例增至217宗 廣東省有14宗<br />\n<br />\n央視報道，截至今日傍晚6時，內地累計報告新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎確診病例217宗，其中武漢198宗，北京5宗，廣東省14宗；疑似病例有7宗，分別來自四川，雲南，上海，廣西及山東。日本通報確診病例一宗，泰國通報確診病例兩宗，南韓通報確診病例一宗。<br />\n<br />\n疫情發生後，黨中央、國務院高度重視。中共中央總書記、國家主席、中央軍委主席習近平作出重要指示，強調全力做好防控工作，將人民群眾生命安全和身體健康放在第一位，採取切實有效措施，堅決遏制疫情蔓延勢頭。<br />\n<br />\n國務院總理李克強主持召開國務院常務會議，進一步部署新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎疫情防控工作，要求有力有效遏制疫情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503822-20200120.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503822-20200120.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9wfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=a7f24090\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503822-20200120.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c151e28e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503822-20200120.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"60058908fd8f32275852e148544f3b024d62c316","tid":1831444,"uid":92188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T11:44:46.000Z","msg":"加多個零"},{"pid":"82f1df081bf14733cc7078634905c5766f0a2696","tid":1831444,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T11:44:59.000Z","msg":"1. 發燒咳嘅人唔會申報<br />\n2. 負責體溫檢查嘅鳩流流（萬幾蚊講野唔正呀嬸）<br />\n3. 根本無一team人（體力好）負責捉人<br />\n4. 睇機個個根本一定話all pass, 佢都唔想接觸病患<br />\n<br />\n你有無見過有人過關因為體溫高而捉住佢？<br />\n我就無見過啦"},{"pid":"be7ff339a710c311cd9428ef9e6e6a5360739da4","tid":1831444,"uid":300388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T11:45:16.000Z","msg":"支爆近了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf4e9ca19bc583d0d76a42ec14c4d2564d89fc15","tid":1831444,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T11:50:57.000Z","msg":"戴口罩是暴徒<br />\n愛國不戴口罩"},{"pid":"bf74adf50c0a8bc1d843faa8c42382e95d00398f","tid":1831444,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60058908fd8f32275852e148544f3b024d62c316","tid":1831444,"uid":92188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T11:44:46.000Z","msg":"加多個零"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T11:54:16.000Z","msg":"起碼兩個零<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}